title: Grammys 2017: All the Best Dressed Celebrities (PHOTOS)
text:

Your favorite musicians and celebrities absolutely rocked the the Grammys 2017 red carpet. 
Take a look at the gallery above to see all the best dressed looks from Music’s Biggest Night — we still can’t get over how hot everyone from Adele to Kristin Cavallari looked!. 
The Grammys 2017 are live on CBS. Check back with Wetpaint for more live coverage.
